title: T-34 Mythical Weapon
description:
T-34 Mythical Weapon
by Robert Michulec

DESCRIPTION:

"The mother of all T34 books!," according to JJ Fedorowicz This book, which was published several years ago, has long been considered the 'definitive' book on the T-34. However, previous editions of the book contained no English translations of the mass of data and images, rendering it difficult to use. Now, we have this NEW edition (ENTIRELY in English) which offers the following: - HARD COVER - LARGE FORMAT - 520 PAGES - 880 BLACK/WHITE PHOTOGRAPHS - 58 PAGES OF 1/35 SCALE DRAWINGS OF ALL VERSIONS OF THE - 36 COLOR INTERIOR PHOTOS - COLOR 3D DRAWINGS - DETAIL PHOTOS OF ALL COMPONENTS OF THE TANK - 20 PAGES IN COLOR
